author: Reuters Editorial
title: Myanmar reports first cases of coronavirus
description: Myanmar reported its first confirmed cases of coronavirus in two men who had recently traveled to the United States and the United Kingdom.
content:
(Reuters) - Myanmar reported its first confirmed cases of coronavirus in two men who had recently traveled to the United States and the United Kingdom.
